int readrec(FILE *fp)

{

float fn;

while (! feof(fp)) {

fread(&reco,sizeof(RECORD),1,fp);

fn=float(reco.open)/1000;

fn=float(reco.low)/1000;

fn=float(reco.close)/1000;

printf("%8lu\n",reco.traca);

}

printf("\n");

return 0;
